title: Week 2: Final CFB Live Show of the 2021-2022 College Football Season.
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and Harry Lyles Jr will go into detail of the recap of the National Championship game between Alabama and Georgia, Caleb Williams' potential landing spot after entering the transfer portal, and what to look forward to for the 2022-2023 college football season.
